text: Ambush at Cimarron Pass is a 1958 American western movie directed by Jodie Copelan and stars Scott Brady, Clint Eastwood, Margia Dean, Irving Bacon and distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:1958 movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:20th Century Fox movies
